{"lastModified":1774445610593,"uri":"c::7819298091::vessel::d5cc4f13-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744","yachtType":["Gulet","Sailing"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece, Turkey, Aegean Sea\n\nDiscover the captivating blend of elegance, comfort, and performance aboard Tigra, a 38-meter steel hull sailing yacht built by Mastori Yachts from Bodrum in 2008, and refitted in 2020. With her modern and stylish interiors by Ken Freivokh Design, perfectly designed for luxury charters in the East Mediterranean. Tigra's spacious and comfortable guest cabins, large deck spaces, and hydraulic lifting swim platform make for an unforgettable experience.\n\nTigra can accommodate up to 10 guests in 5 tastefully designed cabins, including a master suite, a VIP suite, a double cabin, and two twin cabins. The professional and friendly crew of 6 will cater to your every need, ensuring a seamless and enjoyable charter experience.\n\nWith a cruising speed of 10 knots and a maximum speed of 13 knots, Tigra offers great sailing performance while exploring stunning destinations in Turkey, Greece, and the Aegean Sea. For endless entertainment, Tigra is equipped with an array of water toys, including a 5.50m Joker rib tender, donut, sea kayak, stand-up paddleboard, snorkeling gear, wakeboard, water-skis, tube, and fishing gear.\n\nOnboard entertainment features include board games, DVD/CD player, LCD TV, satellite TV system, a sound system throughout the yacht, Wi-Fi internet access, a Bose Music System, and an iPad/iPod/mobile docking station.","blueprint":{"name":"TIGRA","images":["/media/media::image::c::7819298091::vessel::d5cc4f13-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4cbb2230-da08-11ee-9305-2f477901c9fe.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819298091::vessel::d5cc4f13-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4cb72a90-da08-11ee-9305-2f477901c9fe.jpeg/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::c::7819298091::vessel::d5cc4f13-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::4cb8d840-da08-11ee-9305-2f47790